snippet.title: Game & Watch - Green House (c)1982 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
This is Nintendo's Green House, part of the Game & Watch series.  This is another that was emulated a while back, but for which I didn't have a quality video on this channel.  As always thanks to Algestam and co. for the emulation.


Game & Watch artwork for MAME was done by DarthMarino (more recently emulated units) and hydef (units emulated before 2020)
https://drive.google.com/drive/u/1/folders/1vl9O-0jIGCHHY_lrWpOwBtqTXEKsVGOY  DarthMarino 
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1WLKcvynl0ky2mRL1UacA9yaiMTnNs4x5 hydef
